Get the database docker with everything in place:
http://www.oslandia.com/full-spatial-database-power-in-2-lines-en.html

sudo docker run --rm -P --name pggis_test oslandia/pggis /sbin/my_init

get port with:
docker ps

psql -h localhost -p 32768 -U pggis -W pggis

Follow the tutorial from geodjango:
https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/1.9/ref/contrib/gis/tutorial/